N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4202.13 - Credentials or stickers

State Regulations

Credentials issued by the commission to its members, employees and appointees shall be honored by racing associations for admission
at all gates and entrances and to all places within the enclosure of any race
track, and automobiles carrying official windshield stickers of the commission
or other identification issued by the commission shall be permitted and ingress
and egress at any point. Notes
